&lt;p>Completely relying on AI to extract clean vocals is still not quite realistic with current technology; in most cases, manual correction is needed. However, as long as you have enough data, you can always scrape together enough AI-extracted vocals suitable for training.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>AI Covers with Roformer and Applio</title><link>https://blog.yexca.net/en/archives/280/</link><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 03:00:06 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yexca.net/en/archives/280/</guid><description>&lt;div class="notice ">&lt;strong>📢&lt;/strong> This article was translated by gemini-3.5-flash
